<item>
            <title>[LU-1789] Lightweight connection support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1789</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add support for lightweight connection having the following properties:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;no export is added to last_rcvd file, so no recovery is possible&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a new lightweight connection can be established while the target is in recovery&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;locks can still be acquired through this connection, although they won&apos;t be replayed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
